Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,晕船了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好像…突然失去了紧张感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,薰！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不要一脸悲伤 我的小猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我有化作一只飞鸟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我看到你后背长出了纯白的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如梦似幻…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,薰 睁开眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,薰！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是这样
Comment: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,EDJP P
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这是闹哪样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是Hello, Happy World！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,米歇尔 米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,美咲 美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,小美？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,两人睡着都是笑容呢 太好了
